   <concept id="FAR_50_103_7" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">50.103-7</ph> Contract requirements.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d2971e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2998e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Pub. L. 85-804 and E.O. 10789	require that every contract entered into, amended, or modified under	this <xref href="Subpart_50.1.dita#FAR_Subpart_50_1"
                        base="i1066730"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  50.1</xref> shall	contain—</p>
               <ol id="d2971e26" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2998e19">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                A citation of Pub. L. 85-804 and	E.O. 10789;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2998e24">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                A brief	statement of the circumstances justifying the action; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2998e29">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
								                A recital	of the finding that the action will facilitate the national defense.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2998e34">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The authority	in <xref href="50.101-1.dita#FAR_50_101_1"
                        base="i1066737"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">50.101-1</xref>(a) shall not	be used to omit from contracts, when otherwise required, the clauses	at <xref href="52.203-5.dita#FAR_52_203_5"
                        base="i1063306"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.203-5</xref>, Covenant Against	Contingent Fees; <xref href="52.215-2.dita#FAR_52_215_2"
                        base="i1059150"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.215-2</xref>,	Audit and Records-Negotiation; <xref href="52.222-4.dita#FAR_52_222_4"
                        base="i1055350"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-4</xref>,	Contract Work Hours and Safety Standards-Overtime Compensation; <xref href="52.222-6.dita#FAR_52_222_6"
                        base="i1055387"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-6</xref>, Construction	Wage Rate Requirements; <xref href="52.222-10.dita#FAR_52_222_10"
                        base="i1055477"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-10</xref>,	Compliance With Copeland Act Requirements; <xref href="52.222-20.dita#FAR_52_222_20"
                        base="i1055699"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-20</xref>, Contracts for	Materials, Supplies, Articles, and Equipment;<xref href="52.222-26.dita#FAR_52_222_26"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-26</xref>, Equal Opportunity;	and <xref href="52.232-23.dita#FAR_52_232_23"
                        base="i1050093"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.232-23</xref>, Assignment	of Claims.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
